msgstr "用法：%s [选项]... [文件]\n"

#: src/basenc.c:108
msgid "basenc encode or decode FILE, or standard input, to standard output.\n"
msgstr "basenc 编码或解码 <文件> 或标准输入，并输出到标准输出。\n"

#: src/basenc.c:112
#, c-format
msgid "Base%d encode or decode FILE, or standard input, to standard output.\n"
msgstr "Base%d 编码或解码 <文件> 或标准输入，并输出到标准输出。\n"

#: src/basenc.c:120
msgid ""
"      --base64\n"
"         same as 'base64' program (RFC4648 section 4)\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base64\n"
"         与 \"base64\" 程序相同 (RFC4648 section 4)\n"

#: src/basenc.c:124
msgid ""
"      --base64url\n"
"         file- and url-safe base64 (RFC4648 section 5)\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base64url\n"
"         文件安全且 URL 安全的 base64 (RFC4648 section 5)\n"

#: src/basenc.c:128
msgid ""
"      --base58\n"
"         visually unambiguous base58 encoding\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base58\n"
"         视觉上不易混淆的 \"base58\" 编码\n"

#: src/basenc.c:132
msgid ""
"      --base32\n"
"         same as 'base32' program (RFC4648 section 6)\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base32\n"
"         与 \"base32\" 程序相同 (RFC4648 section 6)\n"

#: src/basenc.c:136
msgid ""
"      --base32hex\n"
"         extended hex alphabet base32 (RFC4648 section 7)\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base32hex\n"
"         使用扩展十六进制字母表的 base32 (RFC4648 section 7)\n"

#: src/basenc.c:140
msgid ""
"      --base16\n"
"         hex encoding (RFC4648 section 8)\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base16\n"
"         十六进制编码 (RFC4648 section 8)\n"

#: src/basenc.c:144
msgid ""
"      --base2msbf\n"
"         bit string with most significant bit (msb) first\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base2msbf\n"
"         位字符串，最高有效位 (msb) 最先\n"

#: src/basenc.c:148
msgid ""
"      --base2lsbf\n"
"         bit string with least significant bit (lsb) first\n"
msgstr ""
"      --base2lsbf\n"
"         位字符串，最低有效位 (lsb) 最先\n"

#: src/basenc.c:153
msgid ""
"  -d, --decode\n"
"         decode data\n"
msgstr ""
"  -d, --decode\n"
"         解码数据\n"

#: src/basenc.c:157
msgid ""
"  -i, --ignore-garbage\n"
"         when decoding, ignore non-alphabet characters\n"
msgstr ""
"  -i, --ignore-garbage\n"
"         解码时忽略非字母字符\n"

#: src/basenc.c:161
msgid ""
"  -w, --wrap=COLS\n"
"         wrap encoded lines after COLS character (default 76).\n"
"         Use 0 to disable line wrapping\n"
msgstr ""
"  -w, --wrap=列数\n"
"         在指定的 <列数> 后自动换行（默认为 76）。\n"
"         0 为禁用自动换行\n"

#: src/basenc.c:167
msgid ""
"      --z85\n"
"         ascii85-like encoding (ZeroMQ spec:32/Z85);\n"
"         when encoding, input length must be a multiple of 4;\n"
"         when decoding, input length must be a multiple of 5\n"
msgstr ""
"      --z85\n"
"         类似 ascii85 的编码（ZeroMQ 标准：32/Z85）；\n"
"         编码时，输入长度必须是 4 的倍数；\n"
"         解码时，输入长度必须是 5 的倍数\n"

#: src/basenc.c:177
msgid ""
"\n"
"When decoding, the input may contain newlines in addition to the bytes of\n"
"the formal alphabet.  Use --ignore-garbage to attempt to recover\n"
"from any other non-alphabet bytes in the encoded stream.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"解码时，输入数据除了包含正式的字母表的字节以外，还可能包含一些\n"
"换行符。使用 --ignore-garbage 来使程序在已编码的流中遇到字母表以外的\n"
"字节后尝试恢复执行。\n"

#: src/basenc.c:184
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"The data are encoded as described for the %s alphabet in RFC 4648.\n"
"When decoding, the input may contain newlines in addition to the bytes of\n"
"the formal %s alphabet.  Use --ignore-garbage to attempt to recover\n"
"from any other non-alphabet bytes in the encoded stream.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"数据以 RFC 4648 规定的 %s 字母表的格式进行编码。\n"
"解码时，输入数据除了包含正式的 %s 字母表的字节以外，还可能包含一些\n"
"换行符。使用 --ignore-garbage 来使程序在已编码的流中遇到字母表以外的\n"
"字节后尝试恢复执行。\n"

#: src/basenc.c:879
#, c-format
msgid "invalid input (length must be multiple of 4 characters)"
msgstr "无效的输入（长度必须为 4 字符的整数倍）"

#: src/basenc.c:1479 src/cat.c:972 src/fmt.c:459
#, c-format
msgid "closing standard input"
msgstr "关闭标准输入"

