"Print user and group information for each specified USER,\n"
"or (when USER omitted) for the current process.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"打印每个指定的 <用户> 的用户和组信息，\n"
"当省略 <用户> 时，打印当前进程的用户和组信息。\n"
"\n"

